Georgi Dinkov aka Haidut is just insanely good at taking the 5D chess metabolism stuff and explaining it reasonably even if he gets lost in rants sometimes and then Generative Energy esp. the eps with Dr. Ray Peat himself on are just a show unlike any other I've listened to ever.
